{"tid":1797732,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"冬天行商場必備品","createTime":"2019-12-25T16:14:10.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-25T17:45:24.000Z","uid":137440,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"0db038bfb8dba5869e102afc348ef0230231b004","tid":1797732,"uid":137440,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-25T16:14:10.000Z","msg":"1. 罐裝咖啡/汽水<br />\n<br />\n冬天天氣令人眼瞓<br />\n罐裝咖啡汽水可以<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">醒腦</span></span>提神<br />\n如果加埋<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">長襪</span></span><br />\n大大力吸一啖<br />\n即刻可以眼前一亮<br />\n為咗大家既精神<br />\n一人買一箱都唔過份<br />\n<br />\n2. 保暖防滑手套<br />\n<br />\n冬天商場扶手充滿靜電<br />\n帶返對<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">低調</span></span>既手套<br />\n又可以保護自己對手<br />\n又可以滿足返一個毒撚既期望<br />\n<br />\n3. 扎好一卷既5蚊硬幣<br />\n<br />\n將5,6個5蚊硬幣<br />\n按照自己手既大細<br />\n用一張紙卷起包實<br />\n咁就唔驚冇錢係手<br />\n購物俾錢既時候又快又低調<br />\n只需要用拳頭捉實<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">遞</span></span>向收眼員既<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">面</span></span>前就得<br />\n<br />\n4. 1m-2m手機叉電線<br />\n<br />\n岀街點可以電話冇電<br />\n一條柔軟扎實既叉電線非常重要<br />\niPhone 線既品質就最好<br />\n一有需要就拎岀黎<br />\n幫人<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">叉電</span></span>又得<br />\n自己用又得<br />\n用既時候要小心唔好<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">吊到條頸</span></span><br />\n特別係後面吊到其他人頸係非常危險<br />\n<br />\n5.眼鏡<br />\n<br />\n冬天紫外線特別勁<br />\n帶返副眼鏡<br />\n又可以<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">保護眼睛</span></span><br />\n又可以低調一下<br />\n<br />\n6. Cap帽<br />\n非常低調<br />\n岀街唔洗頭不是夢<strong><strong></strong></strong>"},{"pid":"9f578b7aa82ee5992e8ec0bfae6e0113b8c04000","tid":1797732,"uid":137440,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-25T17:16:26.000Z","msg":"1"},{"pid":"7a497231006fc348fa7a87123613a00b366c6cfe","tid":1797732,"uid":137440,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-25T17:16:36.000Z","msg":"2"},{"pid":"d5332c97e7360ddc65fb1c8396c0a488122017cf","tid":1797732,"uid":137440,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-25T17:16:47.000Z","msg":"3"},{"pid":"fd419870e537a11bb47c67233ff63d401bbd664e","tid":1797732,"uid":137440,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-25T17:16:58.000Z","msg":"4"},{"pid":"fde656ae8a0e890407ddc690ae98ca0c3facd781","tid":1797732,"uid":137440,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-25T17:17:09.000Z","msg":"5"},{"pid":"29caf186f0f24865586c5e4fb3da5137ce1dbc38","tid":1797732,"uid":137440,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-25T17:17:19.000Z","msg":"6"},{"pid":"b098da7160fae0b3ab6941ada0a167c67e4d434b","tid":1797732,"uid":137440,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-25T17:17:30.000Z","msg":"7"},{"pid":"609fa5cadf4ca085cd3839ec46f3c35af1c1a059","tid":1797732,"uid":137440,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-25T17:17:40.000Z","msg":"8"},{"pid":"201ba55fe005d47719159587afdd3b0ec8ea73b4","tid":1797732,"uid":137440,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-25T17:17:50.000Z","msg":"9"},{"pid":"da9ce8dd8a9780d478f3bafaeda1dbce3995df35","tid":1797732,"uid":137440,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-25T17:18:01.000Z","msg":"10"},{"pid":"ece9b410003cf12911b848d29a2eeb946ba67fa1","tid":1797732,"uid":137440,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-25T17:30:31.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"35169a732ba84ba17cbcaa9bd5f0ccaeb73d92f1","tid":1797732,"uid":137440,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-25T17:30:43.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"dd3c97063de683426d8b676b829f2a75138c7a28","tid":1797732,"uid":137440,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-25T17:44:07.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"fff3bcd90f16ea5207ce5af538dc8764cb05